<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,1770,2036]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598">
This species is compared in the original description with 
<taxonomicName authority="Gravenhorst, 1807" authorityName="Gravenhorst" authorityYear="1807" box="[799,1160,1770,1793]" class="Insecta" family="Apionidae" genus="Apion" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pilosellum">
<emphasis box="[799,944,1770,1793]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="598">A. pilosellum</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Gravenhorst" box="[955,1160,1770,1793]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" refString="Gravenhorst, I. L. C. (1807) Vergleichende Uebersicht des Linneischen und einiger neuern zoologischen Systeme, nebst dem eigeschalteten Verzeichnisse der zoologischen Sammlungen des Verfassers und den Beschreibungen neuer Thierarten, die in derselben vorhanden sind. Dieterich, Gottingen, XX + 476 pp." type="book" year="1807">
Gravenhorst, 
<number box="[1104,1160,1770,1793]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" value="1807.0">1807</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, currently a synonym of 
<taxonomicName authority="Herbst, 1797" authorityName="Herbst" authorityYear="1797" box="[151,529,1805,1828]" class="Insecta" family="Brentidae" genus="Eutrichapion" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vorax">
<emphasis box="[151,361,1805,1828]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="598">Eutrichapion vorax</emphasis>
(Herbst, 
<number box="[463,521,1805,1828]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" value="1797.0">1797</number>
)
</taxonomicName>
. In a handwritten note, Gravenhorst himself, after Hellwig’s indication that another 
<taxonomicName box="[151,337,1840,1863]" class="Insecta" family="Apionidae" genus="Apion" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="longirostre">
<emphasis box="[151,337,1840,1863]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="598">Apion longirostre</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was described by Olivier, replaces his 
<taxonomicName box="[754,940,1840,1863]" class="Insecta" family="Apionidae" genus="Apion" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="longirostre">
<emphasis box="[754,940,1840,1863]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="598">Apion longirostre</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
with the name 
<taxonomicName box="[1105,1298,1840,1863]" class="Insecta" family="Apionidae" genus="Apion" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mustelinum">
<emphasis box="[1105,1298,1840,1863]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="598">Apion mustelinum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,1770,2036]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598">
Body vestiture description, shape of rostrum and its close affinity with 
<taxonomicName box="[985,1129,1874,1897]" class="Insecta" family="Apionidae" genus="Apion" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pilosellum">
<emphasis box="[985,1129,1874,1897]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="598">A. pilosellum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
allow for the selection of a specimen of 
<taxonomicName box="[292,385,1909,1932]" class="Insecta" family="Brentidae" genus="Eutrichapion" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vorax">
<emphasis box="[292,385,1909,1932]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="598">E. vorax</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as the 
<typeStatus box="[467,551,1909,1932]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598">neotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName box="[592,740,1909,1932]" class="Insecta" family="Apionidae" genus="Apion" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="longirostre">
<emphasis box="[592,740,1909,1932]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="598">A. longirostre</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. It is a female (fig. 
<number box="[966,979,1909,1932]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" value="3.0">3</number>
) labelled: Thuringia sept. Kyffhäusergeb. Grauer Berg, 
<date box="[313,422,1944,1967]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" value="1959-05-19">
<number box="[313,362,1944,1967]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" value="19.5">19.5</number>
. 
<number box="[365,422,1944,1967]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" value="1959.28">1959</number>
</date>
. 28., Dorn / 
<taxonomicName authority="Hbst., Dieckmann" authorityName="Hbst., Dieckmann" box="[588,944,1944,1967]" class="Insecta" family="Apionidae" genus="Apion" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vorax">
<emphasis box="[588,728,1944,1967]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="598">Apion vorax</emphasis>
Hbst., Dieckmann
</taxonomicName>
det. 
<number box="[1013,1066,1944,1967]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" value="1960.0">1960</number>
/ 
<typeStatus box="[1104,1225,1944,1967]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598">NEOTYPE</typeStatus>
<taxonomicName authority="Gravenhorst, 1807" authorityName="Gravenhorst" authorityYear="1807" class="Insecta" family="Apionidae" genus="Apion" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="longirostre">
<emphasis box="[1241,1435,1944,1967]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="598">Apion longirostre</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Gravenhorst" box="[151,353,1978,2001]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" refString="Gravenhorst, I. L. C. (1807) Vergleichende Uebersicht des Linneischen und einiger neuern zoologischen Systeme, nebst dem eigeschalteten Verzeichnisse der zoologischen Sammlungen des Verfassers und den Beschreibungen neuer Thierarten, die in derselben vorhanden sind. Dieterich, Gottingen, XX + 476 pp." type="book" year="1807">
Gravenhorst, 
<number box="[297,353,1978,2001]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" value="1807.0">1807</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, C. Giusto des. 
<number box="[524,577,1978,2001]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" value="2015.0">2015</number>
/ 
<taxonomicName authority="Herbst, 1797" authorityName="Herbst" authorityYear="1797" box="[600,973,1978,2001]" class="Insecta" family="Brentidae" genus="Eutrichapion" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vorax">
<emphasis box="[600,809,1978,2001]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="598">Eutrichapion vorax</emphasis>
(Herbst, 
<number box="[911,965,1978,2001]" pageId="1" pageNumber="598" value="1797.0">1797</number>
